OBJECTIVE:
The engineering systems have suffered multiple cascading failures. You need
to diagnose the problems by searching through system logs and locating
critical configuration files.

This sector contains three sub-missions in separate directories:
    1. logs/        - Analyze error logs to find failure patterns
    2. schematics/  - Locate critical system files
    3. diagnostics/ - Run comprehensive system analysis

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

COMMAND REFERENCE:

    grep <pattern> <file>     Search for pattern in file
    grep -r <pattern> <dir>   Search recursively in directory
    grep -i <pattern> <file>  Case-insensitive search
    grep -c <pattern> <file>  Count matching lines
    grep -n <pattern> <file>  Show line numbers

    find <dir> -name "*.txt"  Find files by name pattern
    find <dir> -type f        Find only files
    find <dir> -type d        Find only directories

    wc -l <file>              Count lines in file
    wc -w <file>              Count words in file

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

